  <name>Grock</name>
  <summary>Displays geological maps of the UK.</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>Display geological maps of the UK, using data from the British Geological Survey.
	    Allows rock unit names, types and ages to be found easily. Linear features and UK-wide
	    gravitational and magnetic anomaly maps can also be shown.</p>
	</description>
